snippet.title: MEDAL - OF - LEGENDS
snippet.description:
Third Person Shooter with polygon art, your duty is to lead the battle, save world  and become the best shooter and sniper.

Get ready for the assault: It is time for you to rise up and fight for your survival in a zombie apocalypse & dangerous gangs in this heart-stopping third person shooter adventure, save the world !

PLAY NOW ON Itch.io: https://seifeldeen.itch.io/medal-of-legends
